reviewText: DVD in perfect condition. Shipped here pretty fast. Plays on my U.S DVD player and has both dub and sub, which is nice. Great product and delivery all around.

I've read all 9 volumes of the Manga by Hirohiko Araki and his story and art is absolutely amazing  I like the first two dvd's of JoJo's wildly inventive adventures and can't wait to acquire the rest. Hirohiko rocks!!
